{"tid":645504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"證監會擬提高投資者賠償上限","createTime":"2018-04-28T07:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T07:21:51.000Z","uid":4264,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"67dd7efb540bd7f80169a1a948bcddf211837afd","tid":645504,"uid":4264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"證監會於昨日(四月廿七日)公佈開始諮詢市場有關投資者賠償事宜，最主要優化重點包括向每名投資者支付的賠償上限由150,000港元提高至500,000港元，並涵蓋滬股通及深股通的A股。另外，即使賠償上限將會提升，由於現時投資者賠償基金資金充裕，賠償基金徵費仍不會收取，客戶的交易成本亦不會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證券行會唔會大左吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd253c41a6898f5474d6ba426dace7645bd3f975","tid":645504,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3866c7d499171da9a5fd4959cd5905a700f38523","tid":645504,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dd253c41a6898f5474d6ba426dace7645bd3f975","tid":645504,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"牛三"},{"pid":"dd0a6ca7db9df9642de566e0e3a140091ff5a2d5","tid":645504,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3866c7d499171da9a5fd4959cd5905a700f38523","tid":645504,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dd253c41a6898f5474d6ba426dace7645bd3f975","tid":645504,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no